channel.title: Electricity - E/E [Electro Swing, House, EDM]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/eslashe/electricity
My newest track, blending electro swing into the mix of my usual composition style. Listen to that saxophone, it's simply electrifying.
It is also my entry for the [HOUSE MUSIC Challenge](https://disco.auxy.co/t/the-house-music-challenge-march-2018/8078/).
